text: José González (born 4 July 1917) was a Mexican equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1917 births Category:Possibly living people Category:Mexican male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Mexico Category:Equestrians at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Pan American Games medalists in equestrian Category:Pan American Games gold medalists for Mexico Category:Equestrians at the 1955 Pan American Games Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
